        "subject": "LU-2001 llite: Reduce page chache shrinking from kernel",
        "message": "LU-2001 llite: Reduce page chache shrinking from kernel\n\nThis patch increases 'seeks' argument while registering shrinker\nof page cache, so that kernel will avoid shinking pages of Lustre\nwhile possible. This might increase performance of some application.\n\nSigned-off-by: Li Xi <lixi@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: Ia33bca5d700e993517c40c82802f98ec4f1a95ec\n"
